<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>192</hymn_number>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khrihfa ralkap mi hna, Bawi Jesuh bochan in, Thawngthabia a thiang bik
 aupi cio u, Raldohnak le ngaihchiatnak, Rili bang lian ko hmanhseh, Jesuh
 thawngin hodah a kan tei hnga.

[C1]
   Fek te-in dir u si, Teinak tiang kal chin lengmang u si, Bawi bik
   ralkap tha kan si, Bia a kan kam bantukin, Teinak sui luchin kan hmuh cio
   lai.

[V2]
 Jesuh Khrih bochan in, Rulhreu ral do u si, Nan ngun-nam hler u law,
 hmaiah kal u, Bawi Jesuh nih, nan hmaiah ka dir zungzal lai, a ti, A bia
 kam bantuk in kan tei theo lai.

[C2]
   Fek te-in dir u si, Teinak tiang kal chin lengmang u si, Bawi bik
   ralkap tha kan si, Bia a kan kam bantukin, Teinak sui luchin kan hmuh cio
   lai.

[V3]
 Vawlei ngaihchiatnak le, Sifah kan lonh tikah, Vancung khua ah kan
 hawidawtmi hna he, Dong lo-in Pathian thangthatnak hla kan sa zungzal
 lai, Ngaihchiat sifah retheih um ti lai lo.

[C3]
   Fek te-in dir u si, Teinak tiang kal chin lengmang u si, Bawi bik
   ralkap tha kan si, Bia a kan kam bantukin, Teinak sui luchin kan hmuh cio
   lai.</lyrics>
<title>FEK TEIN DIR U SI CH192</title>
</song>